# License and Source Notice

## Upstream SearXNG

This project downloads and builds SearXNG from:

- Repository: `https://github.com/searxng/searxng`
- Pinned revision: `c19d86faa`
- Upstream license: `AGPL-3.0-or-later`
- License text: `https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html`

SearXNG copyright and attribution remain with the SearXNG contributors.

## Wrapper and deployment files

The wrapper and deployment-specific files in this project are intended to be distributed under `AGPL-3.0-or-later` so they can be used together with SearXNG without introducing an incompatible license.

This archive does not vendor the complete SearXNG source tree. During dependency installation, `vendor/searxng_source/build_backend.py` downloads the pinned upstream source archive and builds it into a wheel.

When operating a modified version over a network or distributing it, review the GNU Affero General Public License obligations, including requirements concerning availability of the corresponding source. This notice is informational and is not legal advice.
